So just a simple filled rectangle.

00:01:29.430 --> 00:01:33.045
I'm going to begin by adding the translate method,

00:01:33.045 --> 00:01:38.815
and this moves the reference points of x and y to a different location.

00:01:38.815 --> 00:01:43.660
So let's add ctx to our translate.

00:01:44.540 --> 00:01:47.464
It takes in two parameters,

00:01:47.464 --> 00:01:50.735
